<h1>Exception for operating hours</h1>
<p>Use this window to create and edit an exception to the regular intervals of <a href="../../../../../../alvao-service-desk/implementation/services/operating-hours">operating hours</a>.</p>
<p>Options:</p>
	<ul>
 <li><strong>Start</strong> - enter the date and time from which the exception will take effect.</li>
 <li><strong>End</strong> - enter the date and time until which the exception will be in effect.</li>
 <li><strong>Open</strong> - during the above times the exception will be open.</li>
 <li><strong>Closed</strong> - will be exceptionally closed during the above times.</li>
 <li><strong>Notes</strong> - write an internal note if applicable.</li>
	</ul>


</asp:Content>
